Naja Munthe marks 25 years of fashion history with a significant and important Anniversary Memory Book. This year Naja Munthe can look back on a quarter of a century as one of Danish fashion's most central players, but the look in her eyes is neither sentimental nor nostalgic.
Instead, quite characteristic for the dedicated and enterprising designer, it makes no sense to dwell on the past, however. And she doesn't see her 25 years to draw a line under the past. Absolutely not. Naja keep moving forward, opening new doors, and doing new things, because she is curious, and curiosity keeps leading her down new paths.

Each piece of these premium cashmere sweaters is made of 97% cashmere scraps collected from European garment factories, plus 3% merino wool for strength.
Recycled cashmere is not identical to new cashmere. We collect old cashmere garments and break them down. This normally weakens the yarns making them more susceptible to breakage and pilling, but to tackle this problem, MUNTHE has worked with an Italian mill to spin the recycled cashmere with extra-fine merino wool. Altogether, it is a small line of durable, warm, guilt-free cashmere sweaters with way less ecological impact.
The model is 177 cm in height and wears a size 36. The size measures 108 cm around the chest, 63 cm in length and 80,5 in sleeve check to sleeve end.
Material: 97% Recycled Cashmere and 3% Merino Wool. Care Instructions: Hand wash cold. Dry clean. Flat dry. Iron at medium temperature.

Denne luksuøse kashmir sweater er fremstillet af 97% genanvendeligt kashmir og 3% merino uld. Det er en tidløs, smuk sweater som holder sig elegant i årevis og som altid vil udstråle klassisk elegance.
Genanvendeligt kashmir er ikke det samme som nyt kashmir. MUNTHES genanvendte kashmir er lavet af overskydende fibre fra fremstillingen af kashmirgarn - en ressource, der ellers ville være kasseret. Disse affaldsfibre har samme premium-kvalitet som den konventionelle kashmir, og er kun tilgængelig i begrænsede mængder. Sædvanligt vil sådan en proces svække kvaliteten, og gøre den mere modtagelig for brud og pilling, men netop for at tackle d har MUNTHE fået produceret vores kashmir med 3% merinould.
Sammensætningen af de to naturmaterialer gør blusen ekstraordinært blød, varm og super velegnet til ALLE årstider.
Modellen er 177 cm høj, og er iklædt en størrelse 36. Sweateren måler 108 cm omkring brystet og 63 cm i længden.
Materiale: 97% Recycled Cashmere and 3% Merino Wool.
